main event: Multiple lighted objects were observed in slow flight over a 2 hour period on August 20, 1965.
interesting points: The objects were reported to have blinking lights and were described as consistent with advertising lights., The report was categorized as a sighting of aircraft used for advertising purposes., The observation was made by two individuals in a backyard during a meteor shower., Report stated there was no sound from the objects observed., The report included a response from the Air Force acknowledging the sighting and categorizing it.
witness description: two individuals observing from a backyard
